1
00:00:11,490 --> 00:00:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

2
00:00:12,190 --> 00:00:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't hear?</font>

3
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope!</font>

4
00:00:47,360 --> 00:00:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36"><font color="#4cb7b8">{\an7}Wash <font color="#2e1a12">It</font></font></font></font></font>

5
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36">{\an7}<font color="#2e1a12">All Away</font></font></font></font>

6
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="13"><font color="#042c22"><font face="Times New Roman">Episode<font color="#c76580"> 10    A <font color="#439fa4">Top-Class <font color="#010202">Challenge!</font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

7
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All right, all right.</font>

8
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Good!</font>

9
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, what a disaster.</font>

10
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Just like that.</font>

11
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah. Good, good.</font>

12
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'm sorry.</font>

13
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It even broke the patio roof.</font>

14
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I know it's not actually your fault.</font>

15
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I'm still gonna have to 
add the repair cost to your rent.</font>

16
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

17
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding.</font>

18
00:02:39,390 --> 00:02:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go. Do your thing.</font>

19
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, of course! I'll take care of this.</font>

20
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know plenty of other shops that are 
just as cheap and fast as yours, though.</font>

21
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

22
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding. Kidding.</font>

23
00:02:58,690 --> 00:03:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aji-san is always like this.</i></font>

24
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Arial"><font color="#baae4a">Kinme Cleaning</font></font></b></font>

25
00:03:04,330 --> 00:03:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it is very kind of her to let me 
rent this shop for such low rent.</i></font>

26
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Kinme-san! I really need 
your help with something.</font>

27
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Yagara-san. What happened? 
Shouldn't you be at work?</font>

28
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

29
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen to your shop?</font>

30
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, actually.</font>

31
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the big storm the other day, 
lightning struck a tree in the back.</font>

32
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Are you serious? That's terrible!</font>

33
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That storm sure was something, though.</font>

34
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Power went out at my run-down apartment, 
so nobody could use the shared bath.</font>

35
00:03:44,610 --> 00:03:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that would be inconvenient.</font>

36
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, so what did you 
want to ask me, Yagara-san?</font>

37
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Would you look at this?</font>

38
00:03:57,340 --> 00:04:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Isn't that...</font>

39
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. Sumi ink. I stupidly got some on me.</font>

40
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tried to wipe it off with a tissue, 
but that didn't help at all.</font>

41
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! There's some on your left sleeve too.</font>

42
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must have brushed against the skirt.</font>

43
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? No way!</font>

44
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a break!</font>

45
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things just aren't going my way today. 
And September's only just started.</font>

46
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How...</font>

47
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

48
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long has it been since it got stained?</font>

49
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, let's see. It was this morning, 
so about three hours.</font>

50
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Then we have to deal with it 
right this instant!</font>

51
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

52
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Treating sumi ink stains 
is a race against time!</font>

53
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking from personal experience, 
they're even worse than squid ink.</font>

54
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, squid ink stains are also difficult,</font>

55
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but of all the kinds of stains out there, 
sumi ink is a top-class challenge!</font>

56
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="15"><font color="#6a6265"><font face="Times New Roman">Sumi Ink</font></font></font></font>

57
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="11"><font color="#6a6265"><b>Kinme</b></font></font></font>

58
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="11"><font color="#6a6265"><b>Wakana</b></font></font></font>

59
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="22"><font color="#6a6265"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Challenge!</font></b></font></font></font>

60
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are several different 
kinds of stains.</font>

61
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#5c483d">Resin</font></font></font>

62
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#463830">Water-soluble</font></font></font>

63
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#373f1d">Dye</font></font></font>

64
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#57422e">Bleach</font></font></font>

65
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, time for another knowledge drop!</font>

66
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#463830">Oil-soluble</font></font></font>

67
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can separate them 
into a few main categories.</font>

68
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#3f3631">Protein</font></font></font>

69
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#232121">Insoluble</font></font></font>

70
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#463830">{\an8}Water-soluble</font></font></font>

71
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#5d472d">{\an8}<font size="12">Alcohol</font></font></font></font>

72
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#5d472d">{\an8}<font size="10">Sauce</font></font></font></font>

73
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#3a1e0d">{\an8}<font size="8">Soy Sauce</font></font></font></font>

74
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Water-soluble stains dissolve in water...</font>

75
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#463830">{\an8}Oil-soluble</font></font></font>

76
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#901414">{\an8}<font size="9">Vegetable Oil</font></font></font></font>

77
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#593c26">{\an8}<font size="8">Sesame
Oil</font></font></font></font>

78
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while oil-soluble stains dissolve in oil.</font>

79
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are two main types.</font>

80
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are also stains that 
don't dissolve easily in water or oil.</font>

81
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are called "insoluble," and the 
best-known example of that is sumi ink.</font>

82
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

83
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is extremely difficult to clean 
stains like these at home.</font>

84
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, really?</font>

85
00:05:35,810 --> 00:05:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And ink stains get harder to remove 
the longer they sit untreated.</font>

86
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So before I get started, 
I feel I must warn you</font>

87
00:05:45,330 --> 00:05:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I may not be able 
to remove the ink completely.</font>

88
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is a risk 
a faint stain might remain.</font>

89
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, I will return the clothes 
without charging you for the cleaning.</font>

90
00:05:58,890 --> 00:06:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like to do?</font>

91
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

92
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I want you to clean them!</font>

93
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Huh? Hey!</font>

94
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What's wrong?</font>

95
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... don't take them off here! 
Th-There are people around!</font>

96
00:06:19,610 --> 00:06:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. It's fine! I even brought 
a change of clothes with me.</font>

97
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got to start cleaning 
this instant, right?</font>

98
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:29,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Y-Yagara-san, stop it!</font>

99
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go inside and change in the back!</font>

100
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aww, are you sure?</font>

101
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I will take care of them.</font>

102
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Do your best, Kinme-san.</font>

103
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

104
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can count on Kinme.</font>

105
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, excuse me.</font>

106
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

107
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've finished removing the fallen tree.</font>

108
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much. I appreciate it.</font>

109
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bet.</font>

110
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like two or three tries 
isn't going to do it.</i></font>

111
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, maybe I'll give that a shot.</i></font>

112
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sumi ink is very resistant 
to chemical treatments.</i></font>

113
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can get another material 
to absorb some of the ink</i></font>

114
00:07:59,710 --> 00:08:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and do that over and over...</i></font>

115
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then bit by bit...</i></font>

116
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye, Sensei!</font>

117
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, goodbye! Take care, okay?</font>

118
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel bad! I didn't mean to 
make you come all the way here.</font>

119
00:08:43,090 --> 00:08:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you have your hands full 
with the new term.</font>

120
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate it.</font>

121
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no trouble.</font>

122
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! It's all gone!</font>

123
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing! Thank you!</font>

124
00:08:59,570 --> 00:09:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

125
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm terribly sorry!</font>

126
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

127
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still a faint stain left 
on part of the skirt.</font>

128
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was beyond my abilities as a cleaner.</font>

129
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where?</font>

130
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right here?</font>

131
00:09:15,770 --> 00:09:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can barely even see it! 
It's totally okay.</font>

132
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about it. 
So what do I owe you?</font>

133
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot accept payment.</font>

134
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

135
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was unable to do my job 
and remove it completely.</font>

136
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As such, I cannot accept payment.</font>

137
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about? 
I'm totally satisfied with your work.</font>

138
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

139
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's 99 percent gone!</font>

140
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

141
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She sure can be stubborn.</i></font>

142
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how's this? I'll bring you another 
tasty gift instead. Whaddya say?</font>

143
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

144
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

145
00:10:04,170 --> 00:10:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font color="#4e4741">Praying Mantis
</font></b><font size="16">Year Three, Class One
 Katakuchi Nairo</font></font>

146
00:10:04,170 --> 00:10:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was able to write "praying mantis"!</font>

147
00:10:09,110 --> 00:10:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please take a look!</font>

148
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's Kinme-oneesan! Hello!</font>

149
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? Yagara-san, 
are you and Nairo-chan...</font>

150
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is my homeroom teacher.</font>

151
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a student in my class.</font>

152
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

153
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Katakuchi-san, how many of these have you 
brought me since class this morning?</font>

154
00:10:33,530 --> 00:10:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the fifth one!</font>

155
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fifth one already?</font>

156
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

157
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rather impressive, kiddo!</font>

158
00:10:37,950 --> 00:10:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Does that mean the sumi ink 
on your clothes was from...</font>

159
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No, I spilled it on myself.</font>

160
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

161
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

162
00:10:54,970 --> 00:10:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

163
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much, Hatsuayu-san!</font>

164
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really appreciate you 
coming over to pick me up.</font>

165
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. It's the least I can do.</font>

166
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who invited you 
to lunch, after all.</font>

167
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy I get to see your place 
and enjoy your home cooking!</font>

168
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you've already done so much for me.</font>

169
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Especially for my social skills.</font>

170
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The rest of the family is 
at a memorial service today,</font>

171
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm the only one here.</font>

172
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You decided not to go with them?</font>

173
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yes. We need to have 
at least one person at home.</font>

174
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... right. You see, there's something 
I forgot to ask you about.</font>

175
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

176
00:12:00,410 --> 00:12:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My family has, um...</font>

177
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Stop that right now.</font>

178
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

179
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Er...</font>

180
00:12:27,770 --> 00:12:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You don't have to worry. 
Konatsu and Dai are very gentle.</font>

181
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-Kinme-san, are you 
comfortable around large dogs?</font>

182
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure.</font>

183
00:12:40,830 --> 00:12:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I sweat a lot, 
so I wonder if they smell me.</i></font>

184
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-Kinme-san, what time did you 
have to be back at work?</font>

185
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Half past two,
 so there's still plenty of time.</font>

186
00:12:58,340 --> 00:13:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It'll be ready soon, 
so please wait just a little longer.</font>

187
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

188
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! No! Not... Not there!</font>

189
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Kinme-san, what's the matter?</font>

190
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing. I'm fine.</font>

191
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Big dogs sure are cute.</i></font>

192
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

193
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>B-Because it's my job, I can't help 
but notice the dirt and dog hair</i></font>

194
00:13:46,610 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>on this sofa cover and rug.</i></font>

195
00:13:56,980 --> 00:14:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for waiting. 
Please come this way.</font>

196
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, lovely!</font>

197
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think I've ever had 
authentic paella before!</font>

198
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's actually a quickie recipe 
that uses a rice cooker.</font>

199
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think you can call it authentic.</font>

200
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I was actually getting a little 
worried that you weren't eating properly.</font>

201
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

202
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, remember Hatsushima?</font>

203
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so delicious!</font>

204
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been so long since 
I've had a proper meal!</font>

205
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does Hatsuayu-san usually eat anyway?</i></font>

206
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I'm sorry to make you worry.</font>

207
00:14:45,490 --> 00:14:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, cooking has always been 
one thing that I really enjoy.</font>

208
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've been so busy recently, 
I haven't been able to cook much.</font>

209
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good to know.</font>

210
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if you don't mind, I'll dig in.</font>

211
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!</font>

212
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my. We're being watched.</font>

213
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The carpaccio is delicious too!</font>

214
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fish is sea bass I bought down 
at the seafood market.</font>

215
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? I do a lot of shopping 
at the seafood market too!</font>

216
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I wonder if we've crossed 
paths there before!</font>

217
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to thank you 
for coming today and, well,</font>

218
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">actually, for every day 
I see you at the public bath.</font>

219
00:15:48,930 --> 00:15:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

220
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to your help,</font>

221
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:57,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my social skills are getting better, 
so I'm having less trouble at work.</font>

222
00:15:57,150 --> 00:16:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'm learning to enjoy 
my job a lot more now.</font>

223
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Actually, I don't think I've ever...</font>

224
00:16:07,660 --> 00:16:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">invited a stranger over
 to my place before.</font>

225
00:16:11,710 --> 00:16:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be the first time.</font>

226
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always tended to be withdrawn 
at school, and kind of a homebody,</font>

227
00:16:21,830 --> 00:16:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm a little surprised at myself 
for being able to pull this off.</font>

228
00:16:27,450 --> 00:16:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that since meeting you, 
I've started to change a little.</font>

229
00:16:34,130 --> 00:16:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, gosh. What am I rambling about anyway?</font>

230
00:16:41,010 --> 00:16:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uka-san.</font>

231
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong about one thing.</font>

232
00:16:45,380 --> 00:16:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We aren't strangers anymore. 
We are definitely friends.</font>

233
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the meal! 
It really was a delicious lunch.</font>

234
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not at all. 
Well, I guess I'll drive you back.</font>

235
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where did the dogs go?</font>

236
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

237
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The sliding glass door...</font>

238
00:17:24,830 --> 00:17:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must have totally forgotten to latch it!</font>

239
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you two!
 S-Stop playing with the water!</font>

240
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, now you're both such a mess!</font>

241
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Konatsu, Dai, you really have to behave!</font>

242
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Don't put your paw on my skirt!</font>

243
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me give you a hand.</font>

244
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, what can you do?</font>

245
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye! See you next time!</font>

246
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry it got so late.</font>

247
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, it's fine.</font>

248
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't had a new guest
 over in a long time,</font>

249
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the dogs got a little excited.</font>

250
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They even got your blouse dirty.
 You have to go back to work now, too.</font>

251
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I can change 
into something else.</font>

252
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They took me by surprise at first, 
but the dogs sure were adorable!</i></font>

253
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, about the sofa cover, 
is this really okay with you?</font>

254
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you really 
don't want me to pay?</font>

255
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You treated me to a really 
wonderful time today.</font>

256
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of it as my way of saying thanks.</font>

257
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then thank you very much.</font>

258
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then. Thank you for this.</font>

259
00:20:06,660 --> 00:20:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

260
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I guess I'll see you at the bath.</font>

261
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Thank you again for lunch.</font>

262
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Aji-san! Good afternoon!</font>

263
00:20:27,930 --> 00:20:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

264
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize you were here.</font>

265
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to check out the backyard.</font>

266
00:20:33,990 --> 00:20:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The repair men sure are dragging 
their feet. What are they up to anyway?</font>

267
00:20:38,810 --> 00:20:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish they'd shake 
a leg and get it fixed.</font>

268
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure they're busy around town with 
all the damage caused by the storm.</font>

269
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

270
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heck is that?</font>

271
00:20:58,820 --> 00:21:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. That's a paw print from a dog.</font>

272
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My! So you spent your lunch break 
playing with dogs?</font>

273
00:21:08,830 --> 00:21:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet if I leave my laundry 
for you to wash,</font>

274
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">everything will come back 
with a paw stamp on it.</font>

275
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Same old, same old.</i></font>

276
00:21:19,130 --> 00:21:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

277
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just kidding.</font>

278
00:21:22,690 --> 00:21:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I saw what I needed to, so I'm off.</font>

279
00:21:26,860 --> 00:21:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She tries not to show it,</i></font>

280
00:21:28,870 --> 00:21:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but she was so worried about me 
that she came to check the shop.</i></font>

281
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's already past two thirty now. 
Do you mind?</font>

282
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Of course!</font>

283
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I need to go change, 
so please give me a minute.</font>

284
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#ba834a"><b>Translation:
Editing and Typesetting:</b></font></font></font></font>

285
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#ba834a"><b>Michael Arnold
Ashley Barboza</b></font></font></font></font>

286
00:21:55,830 --> 00:21:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#ba834a"><b>Quality Control:
Translation Check:</b></font></font></font></font>

287
00:21:55,830 --> 00:21:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#ba834a"><b>Riley Dalton
Sriram Gurunathan</b></font></font></font></font>

288
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

289
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wakana-san i-isn't coming over today.</font>

290
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#010202">Episode <font color="#cc808a">11 To Help This <font color="#439fa4">Little Guy <font color="#010202">Out</font></font></font></font></font></font>

291
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:38,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time, "To Help This Little Guy Out."</font>

